</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34073390/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2015-01-21 11:01
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="33460590">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/69535474/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u69535474-9.jpg" alt="新月" class="" /></a>
